#: src/language/supported-features.md:563 src/contributing/architecture.md:56
msgid "Garbage Collection"
msgstr "가비지 컬렉션"

#: src/language/supported-features.md:565
msgid ""
"Perry includes a mark-sweep garbage collector. It runs automatically when "
"memory pressure is detected (~8MB arena blocks), but you can also trigger it "
"manually:"
msgstr "Perry는 mark-sweep 가비지 컬렉터를 포함합니다. 메모리 압박이 감지되면 자동으로 실행되지만 (~8MB 아레나 블록), 수동으로 트리거할 수도 있습니다:"

#: src/language/supported-features.md:567
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"function gcDemo(): void {\n"
"    gc(); // Explicit garbage collection\n"
"}\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/language/supported-features.md:573
msgid ""
"The GC uses conservative stack scanning to find roots and supports arena-"
"allocated objects (arrays, objects) and malloc-allocated objects (strings, "
"closures, promises, BigInts, errors)."
msgstr "GC는 루트를 찾기 위해 보수적인 스택 스캐닝을 사용하며 아레나 할당된 객체(배열, 객체)와 malloc 할당된 객체(문자열, 클로저, Promise, BigInt, 오류)를 지원합니다."

#: src/language/supported-features.md:575
msgid "JSX/TSX"
msgstr "JSX/TSX"

#: src/language/supported-features.md:577
msgid ""
"Perry's parser and HIR understand JSX syntax (parsed via SWC, lowered in "
"`crates/perry-hir/src/jsx.rs`), but the runtime `_jsx` / `_jsxs` symbols are "
"not yet linked, so a `.tsx` file fails at the link stage today. The "
"canonical pattern is the function-call form Perry's UI examples already use "
"(`Text(\"hi\")` instead of `<Text>hi</Text>`)."
msgstr "Perry의 파서와 HIR은 JSX 구문을 이해하지만 (SWC를 통해 파싱, `crates/perry-hir/src/jsx.rs`에서 lower됨), 런타임 `_jsx` / `_jsxs` 심볼은 아직 링크되지 않았으므로 `.tsx` 파일은 링크에서 실패합니다."

#: src/language/supported-features.md:583
msgid ""
"```text\n"
"// Planned JSX shape (parses but doesn't link yet — issue: runtime _jsx "
"symbols):\n"
"\n"
"function Greeting({ name }: { name: string }) {\n"
"  return <Text>{`Hello, ${name}!`}</Text>;\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"<Button onClick={() => console.log(\"clicked\")}>Click me</Button>\n"
"\n"
"<>\n"
"  <Text>Line 1</Text>\n"
"  <Text>Line 2</Text>\n"
"</>\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/language/supported-features.md:598
msgid ""
"JSX elements are transformed to function calls via the `jsx()`/`jsxs()` "
"runtime."
msgstr "JSX 요소는 `jsx()`/`jsxs()` 런타임을 통해 함수 호출로 변환됩니다."

#: src/language/supported-features.md:602
msgid "[Type System](type-system.md) — Type inference and checking"
msgstr "[타입 시스템](type-system.md) — 타입 추론 및 검사"

#: src/language/supported-features.md:603
msgid "[Limitations](limitations.md) — What's not supported yet"
msgstr "[제한 사항](limitations.md) — 아직 지원되지 않는 것"

#: src/language/type-system.md:3
msgid ""
"Perry erases types at compile time, similar to how `tsc` removes type "
"annotations when emitting JavaScript. However, Perry also performs type "
"inference to generate efficient native code."
msgstr "Perry는 `tsc`가 JavaScript를 emit할 때 타입 어노테이션을 제거하는 방식과 유사하게, 컴파일 타임에 타입을 지웁니다. 그러나 Perry는 효율적인 네이티브 코드를 생성하기 위해 타입 추론도 수행합니다."

#: src/language/type-system.md:5
msgid "Type Inference"
msgstr "타입 추론"

#: src/language/type-system.md:7
msgid "Perry infers types from expressions without requiring annotations:"
msgstr "Perry는 어노테이션 없이 표현식에서 타입을 추론합니다:"

#: src/language/type-system.md:9
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"function inferenceBasics(): void {\n"
"    let x = 5;           // inferred as number\n"
"    let s = \"hello\";     // inferred as string\n"
"    let b = true;        // inferred as boolean\n"
"    let arr = [1, 2, 3]; // inferred as number[]\n"
"\n"
"    console.log(`inference: x=${x} s=${s} b=${b} arr_len=${arr.length}`)\n"
"}\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/language/type-system.md:20
msgid "Inference works through:"
msgstr "추론은 다음을 통해 작동합니다:"

#: src/language/type-system.md:21
msgid "**Literal values**: `5` → `number`, `\"hi\"` → `string`"
msgstr "**리터럴 값**: `5` → `number`, `\"hi\"` → `string`"

#: src/language/type-system.md:22
msgid "**Binary operations**: `a + b` where both are numbers → `number`"
msgstr "**이항 연산**: 둘 다 숫자인 `a + b` → `number`"

#: src/language/type-system.md:23
msgid ""
"**Variable propagation**: if `x` is `number`, then `let y = x` is `number`"
msgstr "**변수 전파**: `x`가 `number`라면 `let y = x`는 `number`"

#: src/language/type-system.md:24
msgid ""
"**Method returns**: `\"hello\".trim()` → `string`, `[1,2].length` → `number`"
msgstr "**메서드 반환**: `\"hello\".trim()` → `string`, `[1,2].length` → `number`"

#: src/language/type-system.md:25
msgid ""
"**Function returns**: user-defined function return types are propagated to "
"callers"
msgstr "**함수 반환**: 사용자 정의 함수 반환 타입은 호출자에게 전파됩니다"

#: src/language/type-system.md:27
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"function inferenceFunction(): void {\n"
"    function double(n: number): number {\n"
"        return n * 2;\n"
"    }\n"
"    let result = double(5); // inferred as number\n"
"\n"
"    console.log(`inference-function: result=${result}`)\n"
"}\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/language/type-system.md:38
msgid "Type Annotations"
msgstr "타입 어노테이션"

#: src/language/type-system.md:40
msgid "Standard TypeScript annotations work:"
msgstr "표준 TypeScript 어노테이션이 작동합니다:"

#: src/language/type-system.md:42
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"interface Config {\n"
"    port: number;\n"
"    host: string;\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"function annotations(): void {\n"
"    let name: string = \"Perry\";\n"
"    let count: number = 0;\n"
"    let items: string[] = [];\n"
"\n"
"    function greet(name: string): string {\n"
"        return `Hello, ${name}`;\n"
"    }\n"
"\n"
"    const cfg: Config = { port: 8080, host: \"localhost\" }\n"
"    console.log(`annotations: ${greet(name)} count=${count} items=$"
"{items.length} port=${cfg.port}`)\n"
"}\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/language/type-system.md:62
msgid "Utility Types"
msgstr "유틸리티 타입"

#: src/language/type-system.md:64
msgid ""
"Common TypeScript utility types are erased at compile time (they don't "
"affect code generation):"
msgstr "일반적인 TypeScript 유틸리티 타입은 컴파일 시 제거됩니다 (코드 생성에 영향을 주지 않습니다):"

#: src/language/type-system.md:75
msgid ""
"These are all recognized and erased — they won't cause compilation errors."
msgstr "이들은 모두 인식되고 제거됩니다 — 컴파일 오류를 일으키지 않습니다."

#: src/language/type-system.md:77
msgid "Generics"
msgstr "제네릭"

#: src/language/type-system.md:79
msgid "Generic type parameters are erased:"
msgstr "제네릭 타입 매개변수는 제거됩니다:"

#: src/language/type-system.md:81
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"function identity<T>(value: T): T {\n"
"    return value;\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"class Box<T> {\n"
"    value: T;\n"
"    constructor(value: T) {\n"
"        this.value = value;\n"
"    }\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"function genericsDemo(): void {\n"
"    const box = new Box<number>(42);\n"
"    const id = identity<string>(\"hello\")\n"
"    console.log(`generics: box.value=${box.value} id=${id}`)\n"
"}\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/language/type-system.md:100
msgid ""
"At runtime, all values are NaN-boxed — the generic parameter doesn't affect "
"code generation."
msgstr "런타임에는 모든 값이 NaN 박싱됩니다 — 제네릭 매개변수는 코드 생성에 영향을 주지 않습니다."

#: src/language/type-system.md:102
msgid "Type Checking with `--type-check`"
msgstr "`--type-check`를 사용한 타입 검사"

#: src/language/type-system.md:104
msgid ""
"For stricter type checking, Perry can integrate with Microsoft's TypeScript "
"checker:"
msgstr "더 엄격한 타입 검사를 위해 Perry는 Microsoft의 TypeScript 검사기와 통합할 수 있습니다:"

#: src/language/type-system.md:110
msgid ""
"This resolves cross-file types, interfaces, and generics via an IPC "
"protocol. It falls back gracefully if the type checker is not installed."
msgstr "이는 IPC 프로토콜을 통해 파일 간 타입, 인터페이스, 제네릭을 해결합니다. 타입 검사기가 설치되지 않은 경우 우아하게 폴백합니다."

#: src/language/type-system.md:112
msgid ""
"Without `--type-check`, Perry relies on its own inference engine, which "
"handles common patterns but doesn't perform full TypeScript type checking."
msgstr "`--type-check` 없이는 Perry는 일반적인 패턴을 처리하지만 전체 TypeScript 타입 검사를 수행하지 않는 자체 추론 엔진에 의존합니다."

#: src/language/type-system.md:114
msgid "Union and Intersection Types"
msgstr "Union 및 Intersection 타입"

#: src/language/type-system.md:116
msgid ""
"Union types are recognized syntactically but don't affect code generation:"
msgstr "Union 타입은 구문적으로 인식되지만 코드 생성에 영향을 주지 않습니다:"

#: src/language/type-system.md:118
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"type StringOrNumber = string | number;\n"
"\n"
"function process(value: StringOrNumber) {\n"
"    if (typeof value === \"string\") {\n"
"        console.log(value.toUpperCase());\n"
"    } else {\n"
"        console.log(value + 1);\n"
"    }\n"
"}\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/language/type-system.md:130
msgid "Use `typeof` checks for runtime type narrowing."
msgstr "런타임 타입 좁히기에는 `typeof` 검사를 사용하세요."

#: src/language/type-system.md:132
msgid "Type Guards"
msgstr "타입 가드"

#: src/language/type-system.md:134
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"function isString(value: any): value is string {\n"
"    return typeof value === \"string\";\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"function typeGuardsDemo(): void {\n"
"    const x: any = \"hello\"\n"
"    if (isString(x)) {\n"
"        console.log(x.toUpperCase());\n"
"    }\n"
"}\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/language/type-system.md:147
msgid ""
"The `value is string` annotation is erased, but the `typeof` check works at "
"runtime."
msgstr "`value is string` 어노테이션은 제거되지만 `typeof` 검사는 런타임에 작동합니다."

#: src/language/type-system.md:151
msgid "[Supported Features](supported-features.md) — Complete feature list"
msgstr "[지원되는 기능](supported-features.md) — 전체 기능 목록"

#: src/language/type-system.md:152
msgid "[Limitations](limitations.md) — What's not supported"
msgstr "[제한 사항](limitations.md) — 지원되지 않는 것"

#: src/language/decorators.md:3
msgid ""
"This page states Perry's stance on TypeScript decorators and shows the "
"recommended decorator-free pattern for porting Angular / NestJS / TypeORM "
"code."
msgstr "이 페이지는 TypeScript 데코레이터에 대한 Perry의 입장을 설명하고 Angular / NestJS / TypeORM 코드를 포팅하기 위한 권장 데코레이터 없는 패턴을 보여줍니다."

#: src/language/decorators.md:7
msgid "Stance"
msgstr "입장"

#: src/language/decorators.md:9
msgid ""
"**Perry treats decorators as a legacy compatibility surface, not a language "
"primitive.** The TypeScript ecosystem has been steadily migrating away from "
"decorators since around 2020 — modern frameworks like Drizzle, Hono, tRPC, "
"Prisma, Zod, SolidJS, and Vue 3's Composition API use plain functions and "
"schema-as-code. Even Angular's Ivy compiler already AOT-deletes most "
"decorator metadata at build time, and TC39's new stage-3 decorator spec "
"deliberately drops the runtime type reflection that NestJS and TypeORM rely "
"on."
msgstr "**Perry는 데코레이터를 언어 기본 요소가 아닌 레거시 호환성 표면으로 취급합니다.** TypeScript 생태계는 약 2020년부터 데코레이터에서 꾸준히 멀어지고 있습니다 — 모던 프레임워크들은 명시적 와이어링을 선호합니다."

#: src/language/decorators.md:18
msgid ""
"Perry follows the modern direction: types are erased at compile time (see "
"[Limitations](limitations.md)), there is no `Reflect.metadata`, no "
"`Symbol`\\-keyed metadata side-tables, and no runtime DI container. Code "
"that depends on those facilities does not run on Perry as-is and must be "
"migrated to one of the patterns below."
msgstr "Perry는 모던 방향을 따릅니다: 타입은 컴파일 타임에 지워지며 ([제한 사항](limitations.md) 참조), `Reflect.metadata`도 없고, `Symbol` 키 메타데이터 사이드 테이블도 없으며, 런타임 DI 컨테이너도 없습니다."

#: src/language/decorators.md:24
msgid "What works today"
msgstr "현재 작동하는 것"

#: src/language/decorators.md:26
msgid ""
"Perry parses decorator syntax (legacy / experimental form) and supports "
"**compile-time-only** transforms. The bundled `@log` transform is the "
"canonical example — it rewrites a decorated method into a wrapper that "
"prints entry/exit at compile time, with zero runtime decorator machinery. "
"See `crates/perry-hir/src/decorator_log.rs` for the implementation."
msgstr "Perry는 데코레이터 구문(레거시 / 실험적 형태)을 파싱하고 **컴파일 타임 전용** 변환을 지원합니다. 번들된 `@log` 변환이 정규 예시입니다 — 이는 데코레이트된 메서드를 진입 / 종료 / 오류 로깅으로 다시 작성합니다."

#: src/language/decorators.md:33
msgid "What does not work"
msgstr "작동하지 않는 것"

#: src/language/decorators.md:35
msgid "`Reflect.metadata(...)` and `Reflect.getMetadata(...)`"
msgstr "`Reflect.metadata(...)`와 `Reflect.getMetadata(...)`"

#: src/language/decorators.md:36
msgid "`Symbol(...)` as a metadata key"
msgstr "메타데이터 키로서의 `Symbol(...)`"

#: src/language/decorators.md:37
msgid ""
"`emitDecoratorMetadata`\\-style runtime type capture (constructor parameter "
"types are erased; there is no `design:paramtypes`)"
msgstr "런타임 타입 캡처를 위한 `emitDecoratorMetadata` 스타일 (생성자 매개변수 타입은 지워집니다. `design:paramtypes`는 없습니다)"

#: src/language/decorators.md:39
msgid ""
"Runtime DI containers that resolve dependencies by type (`tsyringe`, "
"NestJS's injector, Angular's root injector)"
msgstr "타입으로 종속성을 해결하는 런타임 DI 컨테이너 (`tsyringe`, NestJS의 injector, Angular의 루트 injector)"

#: src/language/decorators.md:41
msgid "`class-validator`, `type-graphql`, `TypeORM` runtime metadata flows"
msgstr "`class-validator`, `type-graphql`, `TypeORM`의 런타임 메타데이터 플로우"

#: src/language/decorators.md:43
msgid ""
"If your code depends on any of these, the port path is _not_ \"wait for "
"Perry to add Reflect\" — it is to migrate to the explicit-wiring pattern "
"below."
msgstr "코드가 이 중 어느 것에 의존한다면 포트 경로는 _\"Perry가 Reflect를 추가할 때까지 기다리기\"_가 아닙니다 — 아래의 명시적 와이어링 패턴으로 마이그레이션하는 것입니다."

#: src/language/decorators.md:47
msgid "Recommended pattern: explicit construction"
msgstr "권장 패턴: 명시적 생성"

#: src/language/decorators.md:49
msgid ""
"The Perry-native idiom is plain classes wired together in a single "
"`services.ts` module in dependency order. This is how a Go or Rust program "
"would compose services, and it is how decorator-free TS frameworks (Hono, "
"tRPC servers, Drizzle apps) already work."
msgstr "Perry 네이티브 관용구는 종속성 순서로 단일 `services.ts` 모듈에 함께 와이어링된 일반 클래스입니다. 이는 Go 또는 Rust 프로그램이 서비스를 구성하는 방식이며, 데코레이터 없는 TS 프레임워크가 따르는 방식입니다."

#: src/language/decorators.md:54
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"// services.ts\n"
"export const api = new ApiService();\n"
"export const rating = new RatingService(api);\n"
"export const chat = new ChatService(api, rating);\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/language/decorators.md:61
msgid ""
"There is no container, no `@Injectable`, no `providedIn: 'root'` — "
"construction order _is_ the dependency graph, and it is checked by the "
"TypeScript compiler."
msgstr "컨테이너도, `@Injectable`도, `providedIn: 'root'`도 없습니다 — 생성 순서 _가_ 종속성 그래프이며, TypeScript 컴파일러가 검사합니다."

#: src/language/decorators.md:65
msgid "Migration recipe: an Angular service"
msgstr "마이그레이션 레시피: Angular 서비스"

#: src/language/decorators.md:67
msgid ""
"The example below is a real service from sharity-app (`src/app/services/"
"rating.service.ts`, ~80 lines), shown in its original Angular form and "
"ported to Perry."
msgstr "아래 예시는 sharity-app의 실제 서비스 (`src/app/services/rating.service.ts`, 약 80줄)로, 원래 Angular 형식과 Perry로 포팅된 형식으로 보여집니다."

#: src/language/decorators.md:71
msgid "Before — Angular"
msgstr "이전 — Angular"

#: src/language/decorators.md:107
msgid "After — Perry"
msgstr "이후 — Perry"

#: src/language/decorators.md:109
msgid "Three mechanical changes:"
msgstr "세 가지 기계적 변경:"

#: src/language/decorators.md:111
msgid ""
"**Drop `@Injectable`.** It carried no information that the class shape does "
"not already carry."
msgstr "**`@Injectable`을 제거하세요.** 클래스 형태가 이미 가지고 있지 않은 정보는 담지 않았습니다."

#: src/language/decorators.md:113
msgid ""
"**Replace `Observable<T>` with `Promise<T>`** for HTTP calls. Most Angular "
"Observables-from-HTTP are single-value and behave like Promises. (For multi-"
"value streams, use `AsyncIterable`.)"
msgstr "HTTP 호출의 경우 **`Observable<T>`를 `Promise<T>`로 교체**하세요. 대부분의 Angular HTTP-from-Observable은 단일 값이며 Promise처럼 동작합니다. (다중 값 스트림의 경우 `AsyncIterable`을 사용하세요.)"

#: src/language/decorators.md:116
msgid ""
"**Replace constructor-parameter properties** (`private api: ApiService`) "
"with explicit field declarations. Perry supports parameter properties, but "
"explicit fields read more clearly when the class is instantiated by hand "
"rather than by a container."
msgstr "**생성자 매개변수 속성** (`private api: ApiService`)을 명시적 필드 선언으로 교체하세요. Perry는 매개변수 속성을 지원하지만, 클래스가 손으로 와이어링될 때는 명시적 필드가 더 명확하게 읽힙니다."

#: src/language/decorators.md:156
msgid "Wiring"
msgstr "연결"

#: src/language/decorators.md:158
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"// services.ts — single source of truth for service construction\n"
"import { ApiService } from './services/api.service';\n"
"import { RatingService } from './services/rating.service';\n"
"\n"
"export const api = new ApiService();\n"
"export const rating = new RatingService(api);\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/language/decorators.md:167
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"// any consumer\n"
"import { rating } from './services';\n"
"\n"
"const avg = rating.calculateAverageRating(myRatings);\n"
"const list = await rating.getUserRatings('user-123');\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/language/decorators.md:175
msgid ""
"That is the entire migration. The `@Injectable` decorator, the `providedIn: "
"'root'` token, the implicit container lookup — all of it collapses into one "
"`new RatingService(api)` line in `services.ts`."
msgstr "이것이 마이그레이션의 전부입니다. `@Injectable` 데코레이터, `providedIn: 'root'` 토큰, 암묵적 컨테이너 조회 — 이 모든 것이 `services.ts` 안의 단일 `new RatingService(api)` 줄로 축약됩니다."

#: src/language/decorators.md:179
msgid "What about Angular components, NestJS controllers, TypeORM entities?"
msgstr "Angular 컴포넌트, NestJS 컨트롤러, TypeORM 엔티티는 어떻게 합니까?"

#: src/language/decorators.md:181
msgid ""
"Perry does not support these decorator surfaces today, and the runtime "
"metadata they rely on is not on the roadmap. The Path-B option of "
"recognizing `@Component` / `@Controller` / `@Entity` at the compiler level "
"(analogous to Angular Ivy's AOT step) is reserved for if and when a concrete "
"port needs it — see [issue #581](https://github.com/PerryTS/perry/issues/"
"581) for the tracking discussion. For now, the recommendation is the same: "
"drop the decorator, write the equivalent explicit construction, register "
"routes or schema as plain function calls / module-level constants."
msgstr "Perry는 오늘날 이러한 데코레이터 표면을 지원하지 않으며, 그것들이 의존하는 런타임 메타데이터는 로드맵에 없습니다. `@Component` / `@Controller` / `@Entity`를 컴파일러 수준에서 인식하는 Path-B 옵션 (Angular Ivy의 AOT 단계와 유사)은 항상 평가 가능한 옵션으로 남아 있습니다."

#: src/language/decorators.md:192
msgid "Future direction"
msgstr "향후 방향"

#: src/language/decorators.md:194
msgid ""
"If decorators come back into ecosystem fashion, it will be in the [TC39 "
"stage-3 form](https://github.com/tc39/proposal-decorators) — pure compile-"
"time, no metadata reflection — which aligns naturally with Perry's \"types "
"erased, compile to native\" architecture. Any future investment in decorator "
"support will target that spec, not the legacy / experimental form that "
"Angular and NestJS use today."
msgstr "데코레이터가 생태계 트렌드로 다시 돌아온다면, 그것은 [TC39 stage-3 형식](https://github.com/tc39/proposal-decorators) — 순수 컴파일 타임, 메타데이터 리플렉션 없음 — 이 될 것이며, 이는 Perry의 \"타입은 지워지고 네이티브로 컴파일\" 호와 자연스럽게 일치합니다."

#: src/language/limitations.md:3
msgid ""
"Perry compiles a practical subset of TypeScript. This page documents what's "
"not supported or works differently from Node.js/tsc."
msgstr "Perry는 TypeScript의 실용적인 부분 집합을 컴파일합니다. 이 페이지는 지원되지 않거나 Node.js/tsc와 다르게 작동하는 것을 문서화합니다."

#: src/language/limitations.md:5
msgid "No Runtime Type Checking"
msgstr "런타임 타입 검사 없음"

#: src/language/limitations.md:7
msgid ""
"Types are erased at compile time. There is no runtime type system — Perry "
"doesn't generate type guards or runtime type metadata."
msgstr "타입은 컴파일 타임에 지워집니다. 런타임 타입 시스템이 없습니다 — Perry는 타입 가드나 런타임 타입 메타데이터를 생성하지 않습니다."

#: src/language/limitations.md:9
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"function someFunction(): number {\n"
"    return 42\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"function erasedTypes(): void {\n"
"    // These annotations are erased — no runtime effect\n"
"    const x: number = someFunction(); // No runtime check that result is "
"actually a number\n"
"    console.log(`erased-types: x=${x}`)\n"
"}\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/language/limitations.md:21
msgid ""
"Use explicit `typeof` checks where runtime type discrimination is needed."
msgstr "런타임 타입 구분이 필요한 곳에서는 명시적 `typeof` 검사를 사용하세요."

#: src/language/limitations.md:23
msgid "No eval() or Dynamic Code"
msgstr "eval() 또는 동적 코드 없음"

#: src/language/limitations.md:25
msgid ""
"Perry compiles to native code ahead of time. Dynamic code execution is not "
"possible:"
msgstr "Perry는 사전에 네이티브 코드로 컴파일합니다. 동적 코드 실행은 불가능합니다:"

#: src/language/limitations.md:28
msgid ""
"```text\n"
"// Not supported\n"
"eval(\"console.log('hi')\");\n"
"new Function(\"return 42\");\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/language/limitations.md:36
msgid ""
"Perry parses decorator syntax and supports compile-time-only transforms (see "
"the bundled `@log` example), but does not implement the runtime metadata "
"facilities (`Reflect.metadata`, `Symbol`\\-keyed metadata, "
"`emitDecoratorMetadata` type capture) that Angular / NestJS / TypeORM DI "
"containers rely on. See [Decorators](decorators.md) for the full stance and "
"a worked migration recipe."
msgstr "Perry는 데코레이터 구문을 파싱하고 컴파일 타임 전용 변환을 지원합니다 (번들된 `@log` 예시 참조). 그러나 데코레이터 기반 프레임워크 (Angular DI, NestJS 모듈, TypeORM 엔터티)가 의존하는 런타임 메타데이터 기능 (`Reflect.metadata`, `Symbol` 키 메타데이터, `emitDecoratorMetadata` 타입 캡처)은 구현하지 않습니다."

#: src/language/limitations.md:43
msgid "No Reflection"
msgstr "리플렉션 없음"

#: src/language/limitations.md:45
msgid "There is no `Reflect` API or runtime type metadata:"
msgstr "`Reflect` API 또는 런타임 타입 메타데이터가 없습니다:"

#: src/language/limitations.md:48
msgid ""
"```text\n"
"// Not supported\n"
"Reflect.getMetadata(\"design:type\", target, key);\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/language/limitations.md:53
msgid "No Dynamic require()"
msgstr "동적 require() 없음"

#: src/language/limitations.md:55
msgid "Only static imports are supported:"
msgstr "정적 import만 지원됩니다:"

#: src/language/limitations.md:58
msgid ""
"```text\n"
"// Supported\n"
"import { foo } from \"./module\";\n"
"\n"
"// Not supported\n"
"const mod = require(\"./module\");\n"
"const mod = await import(\"./module\");\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/language/limitations.md:67
msgid "No Prototype Manipulation"
msgstr "프로토타입 조작 없음"

#: src/language/limitations.md:69
msgid ""
"Perry compiles classes to fixed structures. Dynamic prototype modification "
"is not supported:"
msgstr "Perry는 클래스를 고정된 구조로 컴파일합니다. 동적 프로토타입 수정은 지원되지 않습니다:"

#: src/language/limitations.md:72
msgid ""
"```text\n"
"// Not supported\n"
"MyClass.prototype.newMethod = function() {};\n"
"Object.setPrototypeOf(obj, proto);\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/language/limitations.md:78
msgid "No Symbol Type"
msgstr "Symbol 타입 없음"

#: src/language/limitations.md:80
msgid "The `Symbol` primitive type is not currently supported:"
msgstr "`Symbol` 원시 타입은 현재 지원되지 않습니다:"

#: src/language/limitations.md:83
msgid ""
"```text\n"
"// Not supported\n"
"const sym = Symbol(\"description\");\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/language/limitations.md:88
msgid "No WeakMap/WeakRef"
msgstr "WeakMap/WeakRef 없음"

#: src/language/limitations.md:90
msgid "Weak references are not implemented:"
msgstr "약한 참조는 구현되지 않았습니다:"

#: src/language/limitations.md:93
msgid ""
"```text\n"
"// Not supported\n"
"const wm = new WeakMap();\n"
"const wr = new WeakRef(obj);\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/language/limitations.md:99
msgid "No Proxy"
msgstr "Proxy 없음"

#: src/language/limitations.md:101
msgid "The `Proxy` object is not supported:"
msgstr "`Proxy` 객체는 지원되지 않습니다:"

#: src/language/limitations.md:104
msgid ""
"```text\n"
"// Not supported\n"
"const proxy = new Proxy(target, handler);\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/language/limitations.md:109
msgid "Limited Error Types"
msgstr "제한된 오류 타입"

#: src/language/limitations.md:111
msgid ""
"`Error` and basic `throw`/`catch` work, but custom error subclasses have "
"limited support:"
msgstr "`Error`와 기본 `throw`/`catch`는 작동하지만 사용자 지정 오류 서브클래스는 제한된 지원을 받습니다:"

#: src/language/limitations.md:123
msgid "Threading Model"
msgstr "스레딩 모델"

#: src/language/limitations.md:125
msgid ""
"Perry supports real multi-threading via `parallelMap` and `spawn` from "
"`perry/thread`. See [Multi-Threading](../threading/overview.md)."
msgstr "Perry는 `perry/thread`의 `parallelMap`과 `spawn`을 통해 실제 멀티스레딩을 지원합니다. [멀티스레딩](../threading/overview.md)을 참조하세요."

#: src/language/limitations.md:127
msgid ""
"Threads do not share mutable state — closures passed to thread primitives "
"cannot capture mutable variables (enforced at compile time). Values are deep-"
"copied across thread boundaries. There is no `SharedArrayBuffer` or "
"`Atomics`."
msgstr "스레드는 변경 가능한 상태를 공유하지 않습니다 — 스레드 프리미티브에 전달된 클로저는 변경 가능한 변수를 캡처할 수 없습니다 (컴파일 타임에 강제됨). 값은 스레드 경계를 가로질러 깊게 복사됩니다. `SharedArrayBuffer`나 `Atomics`는 없습니다."

#: src/language/limitations.md:129
msgid "No Computed Property Names"
msgstr "계산된 속성 이름 없음"

#: src/language/limitations.md:131
msgid "Dynamic property keys in object literals are limited:"
msgstr "객체 리터럴의 동적 속성 키는 제한됩니다:"

#: src/language/limitations.md:134
msgid ""
"```text\n"
"// Supported\n"
"const key = \"name\";\n"
"obj[key] = \"value\";\n"
"\n"
"// Not supported\n"
"const obj = { [key]: \"value\" };\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/language/limitations.md:143
msgid "npm Package Compatibility"
msgstr "npm 패키지 호환성"

#: src/language/limitations.md:145
msgid "Not all npm packages work with Perry:"
msgstr "모든 npm 패키지가 Perry와 작동하는 것은 아닙니다:"

#: src/language/limitations.md:147
msgid ""
"**Natively supported**: ~50 popular packages (fastify, mysql2, redis, etc.) "
"— these are compiled natively. See [Standard Library](../stdlib/overview.md)."
msgstr "**네이티브로 지원**: 약 50개의 인기 패키지 (fastify, mysql2, redis 등) — 이들은 네이티브로 컴파일됩니다. [표준 라이브러리](../stdlib/overview.md)를 참조하세요."

#: src/language/limitations.md:148
msgid ""
"**`compilePackages`**: Pure TS/JS packages can be compiled natively via "
"[configuration](../getting-started/project-config.md)."
msgstr "**`compilePackages`**: 순수 TS/JS 패키지는 [구성](../getting-started/project-config.md)을 통해 네이티브로 컴파일할 수 있습니다."

#: src/language/limitations.md:149
msgid ""
"**Not supported**: Packages requiring native addons (`.node` files), "
"`eval()`, dynamic `require()`, or Node.js internals."
msgstr "**지원되지 않음**: 네이티브 애드온 (`.node` 파일), `eval()`, 동적 `require()`, 또는 Node.js 내부를 필요로 하는 패키지."

#: src/language/limitations.md:151
msgid "Workarounds"
msgstr "회피책"

#: src/language/limitations.md:153
msgid "Dynamic Behavior"
msgstr "동적 동작"

#: src/language/limitations.md:155
msgid ""
"For cases where you need dynamic behavior, use the JavaScript runtime "
"fallback:"
msgstr "동적 동작이 필요한 경우 JavaScript 런타임 폴백을 사용하세요:"

#: src/language/limitations.md:158
msgid ""
"```text\n"
"import { jsEval } from \"perry/jsruntime\";\n"
"// Routes specific code through QuickJS for dynamic evaluation\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/language/limitations.md:163
msgid "Type Narrowing"
msgstr "타입 좁히기"

#: src/language/limitations.md:165
msgid "Since there's no runtime type checking, use explicit checks:"
msgstr "런타임 타입 검사가 없으므로 명시적 검사를 사용하세요:"

#: src/language/limitations.md:167
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"function processValue(value: string | number) {\n"
"    // Instead of relying on type narrowing from generics\n"
"    if (typeof value === \"string\") {\n"
"        // String path\n"
"        console.log(`string path: ${value}`)\n"
"    } else if (typeof value === \"number\") {\n"
"        // Number path\n"
"        console.log(`number path: ${value}`)\n"
"    }\n"
"}\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/language/limitations.md:182
msgid "[Supported Features](supported-features.md) — What does work"
msgstr "[지원되는 기능](supported-features.md) — 작동하는 것"

#: src/language/limitations.md:183
msgid "[Type System](type-system.md) — How types are handled"
msgstr "[타입 시스템](type-system.md) — 타입이 처리되는 방식"

#: src/packages/porting.md:1
msgid "Porting npm Packages"
msgstr "npm 패키지 포팅"

#: src/packages/porting.md:3
msgid ""
"**Status: experimental.** This guide — and the [`port-npm-to-perry` skill]"
"(https://github.com/PerryTS/perry/tree/main/.claude/skills/port-npm-to-"
"perry) that ships alongside it — is a first pass at systematizing what Perry "
"contributors have been doing ad-hoc. Results will vary by package. Feedback "
"at [issue #115](https://github.com/PerryTS/perry/issues/115)."
msgstr "**상태: 실험적.** 이 가이드 — 그리고 함께 제공되는 [`port-npm-to-perry` 스킬](https://github.com/PerryTS/perry/tree/main/.claude/skills/port-npm-to-perry) — 은 Perry 기여자들이 진행 중인 작업을 체계화한 첫 번째 시도입니다."

#: src/packages/porting.md:5
msgid ""
"Perry compiles a practical subset of TypeScript. Most pure TS/JS packages "
"can be pulled into a native compile via `perry.compilePackages`, but some "
"will need small patches to avoid the constructs Perry doesn't support. This "
"page is a field guide for doing that port — by hand, or by driving a coding "
"agent with the prompt template below."
msgstr "Perry는 TypeScript의 실용적인 부분 집합을 컴파일합니다. 대부분의 순수 TS/JS 패키지는 `perry.compilePackages`를 통해 네이티브 컴파일에 통합할 수 있지만, 일부는 Perry가 지원하지 않는 구문을 피하기 위한 작은 패치가 필요합니다. 이 페이지는 그 작업을 위한 현장 가이드입니다."

#: src/packages/porting.md:7
msgid "When porting makes sense"
msgstr "포팅이 의미가 있을 때"

#: src/packages/porting.md:9
msgid "Situation"
msgstr "상황"

#: src/packages/porting.md:9
msgid "Try this first"
msgstr "먼저 시도해 볼 것"

#: src/packages/porting.md:11
msgid "Package uses native addons (`.node` files, `binding.gyp`, `node-gyp`)"
msgstr "패키지가 네이티브 애드온 (`.node` 파일, `binding.gyp`, `node-gyp`)을 사용"

#: src/packages/porting.md:11
msgid ""
"**Don't port** — no path forward. Find an alternative package or use the "
"[QuickJS fallback](../stdlib/overview.md#javascript-runtime-fallback)."
msgstr "**포팅하지 마세요** — 진행할 길이 없습니다. 대체 패키지를 찾거나 [QuickJS 폴백](../stdlib/overview.md#javascript-runtime-fallback)을 사용하세요."

#: src/packages/porting.md:12
msgid "Package is pure TS/JS with only light use of dynamic features"
msgstr "패키지가 동적 기능을 가볍게 사용하는 순수 TS/JS"

#: src/packages/porting.md:12
msgid ""
"**Good candidate.** Add to `compilePackages`, patch whatever trips the "
"compiler."
msgstr "**좋은 후보.** `compilePackages`에 추가하고 컴파일러를 트리거하는 것은 무엇이든 패치하세요."

#: src/packages/porting.md:13
msgid ""
"Package's core API is built on `Proxy` (ORMs, validation DSLs, reactive "
"stores)"
msgstr "패키지의 핵심 API가 `Proxy` 위에 구축됨 (ORM, 검증 DSL, 반응형 스토어)"

#: src/packages/porting.md:13
msgid "**Probably not portable.** The surface Perry-users touch is the Proxy."
msgstr "**아마도 포팅 불가능.** Perry 사용자가 만지는 표면은 Proxy입니다."

#: src/packages/porting.md:14
msgid ""
"Package is pure TS/JS but uses lookbehind regex, `Symbol`, `WeakMap`, etc."
msgstr "패키지가 순수 TS/JS이지만 lookbehind 정규식, `Symbol`, `WeakMap` 등을 사용"

#: src/packages/porting.md:14
msgid "**Patchable.** See [Common gaps](#common-gaps) below."
msgstr "**패치 가능.** 아래의 [일반적인 격차](#common-gaps)를 참조하세요."

#: src/packages/porting.md:16
#, fuzzy
msgid "Known-working packages"
msgstr "npm 패키지 사용하기"

#: src/packages/porting.md:18
msgid "These work end-to-end via `compilePackages` with no patches required:"
msgstr "이들은 패치 없이 `compilePackages`를 통해 처음부터 끝까지 작동합니다:"

#: src/packages/porting.md:20
msgid ""
"**`hono`** — the full hono `app.fetch` surface including middleware (`hono/"
"logger`, `hono/cors`, `hono/jwt`), route groups, JSON responses. Enough for "
"testing and edge-runtime deploys (CF Workers / Vercel Edge / Lambda / Deno "
"Deploy). See [HTTP & Networking → Hono](../stdlib/http.md#hono). Long-lived "
"HTTP server deployment via `@hono/node-server` or hand-rolled `node:http` is "
"currently blocked on [\\#589](https://github.com/PerryTS/perry/issues/589). "
"Closed via issues #421 / #486 / #487 / #577."
msgstr "**`hono`** — 미들웨어 (`hono/logger`, `hono/cors`, `hono/jwt`), 라우트 그룹, JSON 응답을 포함한 전체 hono `app.fetch` 표면. 테스트 및 엣지 런타임 배포 (CF Workers / Vercel Edge / Lambda / Deno Deploy)에 충분합니다. [HTTP & 네트워킹 → Hono](../stdlib/http.md#hono)를 참조하세요."

#: src/packages/porting.md:27
msgid ""
"**`@bradenmacdonald/s3-lite-client`** — pure-TS AWS S3 / S3-compatible "
"storage client (R2, MinIO, B2, Spaces, Supabase, LocalStack). Full SigV4 "
"signing chain (Put/Get/Head/Delete/List + presigned URLs) verified byte-"
"identical to `bun`. See [HTTP & Networking → AWS S3](../stdlib/http.md#aws-"
"s3--s3-compatible-object-storage) for the usage pattern. Closed via [\\#551]"
"(https://github.com/PerryTS/perry/issues/551)"
msgstr "**`@bradenmacdonald/s3-lite-client`** — 순수 TS AWS S3 / S3 호환 스토리지 클라이언트 (R2, MinIO, B2, Spaces, Supabase, LocalStack). `bun`과 바이트 단위로 동일하게 검증된 전체 SigV4 서명 체인 (Put/Get/Head/Delete/List + 사전 서명된 URL). [HTTP & 네트워킹 → S3](../stdlib/http.md#aws-s3--s3-호환-객체-저장소)를 참조하세요."

#: src/packages/porting.md:32
msgid ""
"15 general-purpose stdlib fixes (Web Crypto, Web Streams subclassing, typed-"
"array marshalling, `extends Error`, namespace imports, etc.)."
msgstr "15개의 일반 목적 stdlib 수정 (Web Crypto, Web Streams 서브클래싱, 타입 배열 마샬링, `extends Error`, 네임스페이스 import 등)."

#: src/packages/porting.md:35
msgid "The workflow"
msgstr "워크플로우"

#: src/packages/porting.md:37
msgid "1. Add it to `compilePackages`"
msgstr "1. `compilePackages`에 추가"

#: src/packages/porting.md:39
msgid "In your project's `package.json`:"
msgstr "프로젝트의 `package.json`에서:"

#: src/packages/porting.md:49
msgid ""
"This is what tells Perry to pull the package into the native compile instead "
"of routing it through a JavaScript runtime. See [Project Configuration](../"
"getting-started/project-config.md#compilepackages) for the full semantics — "
"including how first-resolved directories get cached so transitive copies "
"dedup."
msgstr "이는 Perry에게 패키지를 JavaScript 런타임으로 라우팅하는 대신 네이티브 컴파일에 통합하도록 지시하는 것입니다. 첫 번째 해결된 디렉터리가 후속 import에 대해 어떻게 캐시되는지 등을 포함한 전체 의미는 [프로젝트 구성](../getting-started/project-config.md#compilepackages)을 참조하세요."

#: src/packages/porting.md:51
msgid "2. Try compiling"
msgstr "2. 컴파일 시도"

#: src/packages/porting.md:57
msgid ""
"Most of the time this is where you find out what's actually broken. Compile-"
"time errors cite a file:line in the package — that's your patch list."
msgstr "대부분의 경우 여기서 실제로 무엇이 깨졌는지 알게 됩니다. 컴파일 타임 오류는 패키지 내의 file:line을 인용합니다 — 그것이 당신의 패치 목록입니다."

#: src/packages/porting.md:59
msgid "3. Patch the gaps"
msgstr "3. 격차 패치"

#: src/packages/porting.md:61
msgid ""
"See [Common gaps](#common-gaps) for the typical fixes. Keep patches minimal "
"and localized — the goal is a clean compile, not a refactor."
msgstr "일반적인 수정에 대해서는 [일반적인 격차](#common-gaps)를 참조하세요. 패치는 최소화하고 지역화하세요 — 목표는 클린 컴파일이지 리팩토링이 아닙니다."

#: src/packages/porting.md:63
msgid ""
"**Record each patch** in a file at your project root (convention: `perry-"
"patches/<package>.md`) so you can reapply them after `npm install` blows "
"them away. Until `compilePackages` grows a native patch-file convention, "
"this is the one bit of maintenance overhead."
msgstr "각 패치를 프로젝트 루트의 파일에 **기록하세요** (관례: `perry-patches/<package>.md`). `npm install`이 패치를 날려버린 후에 다시 적용할 수 있도록 하기 위함입니다. `compilePackages`가 네이티브 패치 파일 관례를 갖출 때까지, 이는 시간이 지남에 따라 사라지지 않게 하는 데 필요한 한 가지 유지보수 작업입니다."

#: src/packages/porting.md:65
msgid "4. Re-check after each compile"
msgstr "4. 각 컴파일 후 다시 확인"

#: src/packages/porting.md:67
msgid ""
"Iterate: compile, patch the next error, compile again. Don't try to catch "
"everything in a single pass — some errors only surface after earlier ones "
"are fixed."
msgstr "반복하세요: 컴파일하고, 다음 오류를 패치하고, 다시 컴파일하세요. 단일 통과로 모든 것을 잡으려고 하지 마세요 — 일부 오류는 이전 오류가 수정된 후에만 표면화됩니다."

#: src/packages/porting.md:69
msgid "Common gaps"
msgstr "일반적인 격차"

#: src/packages/porting.md:71
msgid ""
"Perry's [full limitations list](../language/limitations.md) is the canonical "
"reference. In practice, these are the ones you hit when porting:"
msgstr "Perry의 [전체 제한 사항 목록](../language/limitations.md)이 정규 참조입니다. 실제로 포팅할 때 부딪히는 것들은 다음과 같습니다:"

#: src/packages/porting.md:73
msgid "Lookbehind regex"
msgstr "Lookbehind 정규식"

#: src/packages/porting.md:75
msgid ""
"Perry uses Rust's `regex` crate, which doesn't support lookbehind (`(?"
"<=…)` / `(?<!…)`)."
msgstr "Perry는 lookbehind (`(?<=…)` / `(?<!…)`)를 지원하지 않는 Rust의 `regex` 크레이트를 사용합니다."

#: src/packages/porting.md:77
msgid ""
"```text\n"
"// Not supported\n"
"str.match(/(?<=prefix)\\w+/);\n"
"\n"
"// Rewrite — capture the prefix and slice\n"
"const m = str.match(/prefix(\\w+)/);\n"
"const rest = m ? m[1] : null;\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/packages/porting.md:86
msgid "`Symbol`"
msgstr ""

#: src/packages/porting.md:88
msgid ""
"Not supported as a primitive. When a package uses `Symbol` as a sentinel "
"(the common case — e.g., for unique keys in a registry), swap for a string:"
msgstr "프리미티브로 지원되지 않습니다. 패키지가 `Symbol`을 sentinel로 사용하는 경우 (일반적인 경우 — 예: 레지스트리에서 고유 키용), 문자열로 교체하세요:"

#: src/packages/porting.md:90
msgid ""
"```text\n"
"// Before\n"
"const REGISTRY_KEY = Symbol(\"registry\");\n"
"\n"
"// After\n"
"const REGISTRY_KEY = \"__pkg_registry__\";\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/packages/porting.md:98
msgid ""
"When `Symbol` is used to implement `Symbol.iterator`/`Symbol.asyncIterator`, "
"check whether the iteration is actually reached in your use case — often the "
"class has a `for`\\-loop method alongside the iterator and you can ignore "
"the iterator path."
msgstr "`Symbol`이 `Symbol.iterator`/`Symbol.asyncIterator`를 구현하는 데 사용되는 경우, 사용 사례에서 반복이 실제로 도달되는지 확인하세요 — 종종 클래스에는 이터레이터 옆에 `for` 루프 메서드가 있어 이터레이터 경로를 무시할 수 있습니다."

#: src/packages/porting.md:100
msgid "`Proxy`, `Reflect`"
msgstr "`Proxy`, `Reflect`"

#: src/packages/porting.md:102
msgid ""
"Not supported. These are usually load-bearing for the package's public API, "
"so porting is often not feasible. If the `Proxy` is only in an optional path "
"(e.g., dev-mode warnings), delete that branch."
msgstr "지원되지 않습니다. 이들은 보통 패키지의 공개 API에서 핵심을 담당하므로 포팅이 실현 가능하지 않은 경우가 많습니다. `Proxy`가 선택적 경로에만 있다면 (예: dev 모드 경고), 그 분기를 삭제하세요."

#: src/packages/porting.md:104
msgid "`WeakMap` / `WeakRef` / `FinalizationRegistry`"
msgstr "`WeakMap` / `WeakRef` / `FinalizationRegistry`"

#: src/packages/porting.md:106
msgid ""
"Not implemented. Swap `WeakMap` for a regular `Map` if the GC semantics "
"aren't critical for correctness (most caches can tolerate this — they'll "
"just hold references slightly longer)."
msgstr "구현되지 않았습니다. GC 의미가 정확성에 중요하지 않다면 `WeakMap`을 일반 `Map`으로 교체하세요 (대부분의 캐시는 이를 견딜 수 있습니다 — 단지 참조를 약간 더 오래 유지할 뿐입니다)."

#: src/packages/porting.md:110
msgid ""
"```text\n"
"// Not supported\n"
"@Component\n"
"class Foo {}\n"
"\n"
"// Remove the decorator and inline the behavior, or use a factory function\n"
"const Foo = Component(class Foo {});\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/packages/porting.md:119
msgid "Dynamic `require()` / `await import(…)`"
msgstr "동적 `require()` / `await import(…)`"

#: src/packages/porting.md:121
msgid ""
"Perry only supports static imports. If a package branches on `typeof "
"require !== \"undefined\"` for a Node/browser split, pick the branch that "
"works natively and delete the other."
msgstr "Perry는 정적 import만 지원합니다. 패키지가 Node/브라우저 분기를 위해 `typeof require !== \"undefined\"`로 분기한다면, 네이티브로 작동하는 분기를 선택하고 다른 것은 삭제하세요."

#: src/packages/porting.md:123
msgid "Prototype manipulation"
msgstr "프로토타입 조작"

#: src/packages/porting.md:125
msgid ""
"```text\n"
"// Not supported\n"
"Object.setPrototypeOf(obj, proto);\n"
"MyClass.prototype.newMethod = function() {};\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/packages/porting.md:131
msgid ""
"Usually appears in fallback shims for older runtimes. Often dead code in the "
"Perry path — just delete it."
msgstr "보통 이전 런타임용 폴백 shim에 나타납니다. Perry 경로에서는 종종 죽은 코드입니다 — 그냥 삭제하세요."

#: src/packages/porting.md:133
msgid "Computed property keys in object literals"
msgstr "객체 리터럴의 계산된 속성 키"

#: src/packages/porting.md:135
msgid ""
"```text\n"
"// Not supported\n"
"const obj = { [key]: value };\n"
"\n"
"// Rewrite\n"
"const obj: Record<string, V> = {};\n"
"obj[key] = value;\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/packages/porting.md:144
msgid "Using a coding agent"
msgstr "코딩 에이전트 사용"

#: src/packages/porting.md:146
msgid ""
"A general coding agent (Claude Code, Cursor, Codex, Aider) can drive most of "
"this workflow. If you're using a skill-aware agent, invoke the [`port-npm-to-"
"perry` skill](https://github.com/PerryTS/perry/tree/main/.claude/skills/port-"
"npm-to-perry) directly. Otherwise, paste this prompt:"
msgstr "일반 코딩 에이전트 (Claude Code, Cursor, Codex, Aider)는 이 워크플로우의 대부분을 운전할 수 있습니다. 스킬 인식 에이전트를 사용하는 경우, [`port-npm-to-perry` 스킬](https://github.com/PerryTS/perry/tree/main/.claude/skills/port-npm-to-perry)을 직접 호출하세요."

#: src/packages/porting.md:148
msgid ""
"```\n"
"I want to port the npm package <NAME> to run under Perry\n"
"(https://github.com/PerryTS/perry). Perry compiles a subset of TypeScript\n"
"natively; the subset's gaps are documented at\n"
"https://github.com/PerryTS/perry/blob/main/docs/src/language/"
"limitations.md.\n"
"\n"
"Please:\n"
"\n"
"1. Read the package at node_modules/<NAME>/. Check package.json for\n"
"   native addons (binding.gyp, gypfile, prebuilds/ — stop if present).\n"
"2. Scan for unsupported constructs: eval, new Function, dynamic require,\n"
"   Symbol, Proxy, WeakMap, WeakRef, Reflect, decorators, lookbehind\n"
"   regex (?<= / ?<!), Object.setPrototypeOf, computed property keys.\n"
"3. Report a triage: what rules the package out vs. what's patchable.\n"
"4. If patchable: add the package to perry.compilePackages in\n"
"   package.json, apply minimal localized patches, and record each\n"
"   patch in perry-patches/<NAME>.md.\n"
"5. Verify by running `perry compile` against a small file that imports\n"
"   the package.\n"
"\n"
"Don't patch blindly — a grep hit inside a string or comment isn't real.\n"
"Show me the triage before applying substantial patches.\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/packages/porting.md:172
msgid ""
"This is intentionally an agent-agnostic prompt — it'll work with any "
"competent coding agent. The skill version bundles the same instructions with "
"richer context and is auto-discovered by Claude Code."
msgstr "이는 의도적으로 에이전트에 구애받지 않는 프롬프트입니다 — 모든 능숙한 코딩 에이전트와 작동합니다. 스킬 버전은 더 풍부한 컨텍스트로 같은 지침을 묶고 Claude Code에 의해 자동 검색됩니다."

#: src/packages/porting.md:174
msgid "Giving feedback"
msgstr "피드백 제공"

#: src/packages/porting.md:176
msgid ""
"This whole workflow is experimental. If a port fails in a way that feels "
"like Perry should handle it — or if the guide misses a common gap — please "
"comment on [issue #115](https://github.com/PerryTS/perry/issues/115) so we "
"can iterate."
msgstr "이 전체 워크플로우는 실험적입니다. Perry가 처리해야 할 것처럼 느껴지는 방식으로 포트가 실패하거나 — 또는 가이드가 일반적인 격차를 놓치는 경우 — 반복할 수 있도록 [issue #115](https://github.com/PerryTS/perry/issues/115)에 댓글을 남겨주세요."

#: src/native-libraries/overview.md:1
msgid "Native bindings — overview"
msgstr "네이티브 바인딩 — 개요"

#: src/native-libraries/overview.md:3
msgid ""
"Perry compiles TypeScript to native executables. When user code says `import "
"{ createConnection } from \"mysql2\"`, the call doesn't bottom out in "
"JavaScript-engine glue — it lands on a Rust function that's been linked into "
"the binary as `extern \"C\"`. This page is the map of how that works end-to-"
"end."
msgstr "Perry는 TypeScript를 네이티브 실행 파일로 컴파일합니다. 사용자 코드가 `import { createConnection } from \"mysql2\"`라고 말할 때, 호출은 JavaScript 엔진 글루로 마무리되지 않습니다 — 바이너리에 `extern \"C\"`로 링크된 Rust 함수에 도달합니다. 이 페이지는 그것이 어떻게 작동하는지, 그리고 자신만의 바인딩을 어떻게 게시하는지 설명합니다."

#: src/native-libraries/overview.md:9
msgid "The big picture"
msgstr "큰 그림"

#: src/native-libraries/overview.md:11
msgid "There are four layers, from most stable to most flexible:"
msgstr "가장 안정적인 것부터 가장 유연한 것까지 네 개의 레이어가 있습니다:"

#: src/native-libraries/overview.md:13
msgid ""
"```text\n"
"┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n"
"│  Layer 4: User TypeScript                                        │\n"
"│    import { createConnection } from \"mysql2\";                     │\n"
"│    const c = await createConnection({ host, user, password });    │\n"
"│    const [rows] = await c.query(\"SELECT 1\");                      │\n"
"└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n"
"                              │\n"
"                              │ resolved at compile time → maps to\n"
"                              │ js_mysql2_* extern \"C\" symbols\n"
"                              ▼\n"
"┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n"
"│  Layer 3: Bindings packages                                      │\n"
"│    Three sources, queried in this order:                          │\n"
"│                                                                   │\n"
"│    a. node_modules/<name>/ with perry.nativeLibrary               │\n"
"│       → the user installed an external binding via                │\n"
"│         `bun add @scope/<name>`. Wins over (b) and (c).           │\n"
"│                                                                   │\n"
"│    b. node_modules/<name>/ without perry.nativeLibrary            │\n"
"│       → fall through to V8/JS interpretation.                     │\n"
"│                                                                   │\n"
"│    c. well-known table (well_known_bindings.toml)                 │\n"
"│       → Perry ships the binding in its install. ~30 names like   │\n"
"│         dotenv / mysql2 / axios / ws / lru-cache / commander.     │\n"
"│                                                                   │\n"
"│    d. nothing matches → resolution error at compile time.         │\n"
"└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n"
"                              │\n"
"                              │ all wrapper crates depend on this:\n"
"                              ▼\n"
"┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n"
"│  Layer 2: perry-ffi crate (the stable ABI)                       │\n"
"│    pub fn alloc_string(s: &str) -> JsString                       │\n"
"│    pub fn read_string(JsString) -> Option<&'static str>           │\n"
"│    pub struct JsValue(u64); JsPromise; JsClosure; ...             │\n"
"│                                                                   │\n"
"│    9 surface dimensions: strings, async/Promise, handle           │\n"
"│    registry, JsValue/objects/arrays, binary bytes, closures,     │\n"
"│    GC root scanner, BigInt, Buffer, JSON-stringify, event-pump.  │\n"
"│                                                                   │\n"
"│    Wrapper authors depend ONLY on perry-ffi. perry-runtime's     │\n"
"│    internals (NaN-box tags, struct layouts) can change between    │\n"
"│    releases without breaking wrappers.                            │\n"
"└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n"
"                              │\n"
"                              │ implementation detail of:\n"
"                              ▼\n"
"┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n"
"│  Layer 1: perry-runtime / perry-stdlib internals                 │\n"
"│    StringHeader / ArrayHeader / ObjectHeader layouts, NaN-      │\n"
"│    boxing tags, generational GC, arena allocator, async runtime,│\n"
"│    the 30+ in-tree native modules (perry/ui, perry/thread, ...).│\n"
"│    Free to change between Perry releases — the perry-ffi semver  │\n"
"│    is the only stable contract.                                  │\n"
"└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/native-libraries/overview.md:71
msgid ""
"The whole point: **anyone can publish a binding**. A third-party crate ships "
"an npm package containing a Rust crate, a `package.json` with a "
"`perry.nativeLibrary` block, and prebuilt staticlibs. Users `bun add` it. "
"Perry's compiler picks it up automatically. No PR to the Perry repo, no "
"central registry approval, no `@perryts/` namespace required."
msgstr "전체 요점: **누구나 바인딩을 게시할 수 있습니다**. 서드파티 크레이트는 Rust 크레이트, `perry.nativeLibrary` 블록이 있는 `package.json`, 사전 빌드된 staticlib을 포함하는 npm 패키지를 출하합니다. 사용자가 `bun add` 합니다. Perry의 컴파일러가 자동으로 그것을 가져옵니다."

#: src/native-libraries/overview.md:78
msgid "Worked example: `import { createConnection } from \"mysql2\"`"
msgstr "작업 예시: `import { createConnection } from \"mysql2\"`"

#: src/native-libraries/overview.md:80
msgid ""
"Step by step, what happens when you `perry compile` a program with that "
"import:"
msgstr "그 import가 있는 프로그램을 `perry compile`할 때 무슨 일이 일어나는지 단계별로:"

#: src/native-libraries/overview.md:83
msgid "1. Module resolution"
msgstr "1. 모듈 해결"

#: src/native-libraries/overview.md:85
msgid ""
"Perry's resolver ([`crates/perry/src/commands/compile/resolve.rs`](https://"
"github.com/PerryTS/perry/blob/main/crates/perry/src/commands/compile/"
"resolve.rs)) walks each search path looking for `node_modules/mysql2/`:"
msgstr "Perry의 리졸버 ([`crates/perry/src/commands/compile/resolve.rs`](https://github.com/PerryTS/perry/blob/main/crates/perry/src/commands/compile/resolve.rs))는 각 검색 경로를 따라 `node_modules/mysql2/`를 찾습니다:"

#: src/native-libraries/overview.md:89
msgid ""
"**If `node_modules/mysql2/package.json` exists with a `perry.nativeLibrary` "
"block**: parse the manifest, treat the package as a native binding. Skip "
"layers (c) and (d)."
msgstr "**`node_modules/mysql2/package.json`이 `perry.nativeLibrary` 블록과 함께 존재하는 경우**: 매니페스트를 파싱하고 패키지를 네이티브 바인딩으로 취급합니다. 레이어 (c)와 (d)를 건너뜁니다."

#: src/native-libraries/overview.md:92
msgid ""
"**If `node_modules/mysql2/` exists without a `perry.nativeLibrary` block**: "
"this is a JS-only npm package; fall through to the V8 / JS interpretation "
"path (separate compilation flow)."
msgstr "**`node_modules/mysql2/`가 `perry.nativeLibrary` 블록 없이 존재하는 경우**: 이는 JS 전용 npm 패키지입니다. V8 / JS 해석 경로로 떨어집니다 (별도의 컴파일 흐름)."

#: src/native-libraries/overview.md:96
msgid ""
"**If `node_modules/mysql2/` doesn't exist at all**: consult the **well-known "
"table** at [`crates/perry/well_known_bindings.toml`](https://github.com/"
"PerryTS/perry/blob/main/crates/perry/well_known_bindings.toml). The table "
"maps `mysql2` → `perry-ext-mysql2` (a Rust crate that ships in the Perry "
"install). The user didn't `npm install` anything; Perry handles it."
msgstr "**`node_modules/mysql2/`가 전혀 존재하지 않는 경우**: [`crates/perry/well_known_bindings.toml`](https://github.com/PerryTS/perry/blob/main/crates/perry/well_known_bindings.toml)에 있는 **well-known 테이블**을 참고합니다. 테이블은 `mysql2`를 `perry-ext-mysql2` 크레이트로 매핑합니다."

#: src/native-libraries/overview.md:102
msgid "**If nothing matches**: compile error pointing at the import line."
msgstr "**일치하는 것이 없는 경우**: import 줄을 가리키는 컴파일 오류."

#: src/native-libraries/overview.md:104
msgid "2. ABI version check"
msgstr "2. ABI 버전 검사"

#: src/native-libraries/overview.md:106
msgid ""
"If the resolved binding has a `perry.nativeLibrary.abiVersion` field "
"(required from v0.6.0 onwards; warning-only in v0.5.x), Perry verifies the "
"declared semver range covers the bundled `perry-ffi` version. A binding "
"declaring `\"0.5\"` loads under any `0.5.x` Perry; one declaring `\"^1.0\"` "
"loads only under `1.x`. Mismatches are a hard compile error with a recipe "
"pointing at the offending package."
msgstr "해결된 바인딩에 `perry.nativeLibrary.abiVersion` 필드가 있다면 (v0.6.0부터 필수, v0.5.x에서는 경고만), Perry는 선언된 semver 범위가 번들된 `perry-ffi` 버전을 다루는지 확인합니다. `\"0.5\"`를 선언하는 바인딩은 perry-ffi 0.5.x를 출하하는 모든 Perry에서 로드되며, 0.6.0에서는 거부됩니다."

#: src/native-libraries/overview.md:113
msgid "See [`manifest-v1.md`](manifest-v1.md) for the full schema."
msgstr "전체 스키마는 [`manifest-v1.md`](manifest-v1.md)를 참조하세요."

#: src/native-libraries/overview.md:115
msgid "3. Symbol mapping"
msgstr "3. 심볼 매핑"

#: src/native-libraries/overview.md:117
msgid ""
"The manifest's `functions[]` block lists every `extern \"C\"` symbol the "
"staticlib exports plus their TypeScript-visible signature:"
msgstr "매니페스트의 `functions[]` 블록은 staticlib이 내보내는 모든 `extern \"C\"` 심볼과 그들의 TypeScript에서 보이는 시그니처를 나열합니다:"

