msgstr "boolean on/off 스위치."

#: src/ui/widgets.md:156
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"// demonstrates: Toggle widget bound to State\n"
"// docs: docs/src/ui/widgets.md\n"
"// platforms: macos, linux, windows\n"
