msgid "Return type — typically `\"f64\"` (NaN-boxed value or promise handle)"
msgstr "반환 타입 — 일반적으로 `\"f64\"` (NaN-boxed 값 또는 Promise 핸들)"

#: src/plugins/native-extensions.md:98
